## ğŸ”§ TypeScript Tokens (semantic.ts)

**Use ONLY for:**
- âœ… Canvas/WebGL
- âœ… Chart libraries (Recharts, Chart.js)
- âœ… Programmatic color logic

### Canvas Example

```typescript
import { semantic } from '$shared/styles/tokens';

function draw(ctx: CanvasRenderingContext2D) {
  ctx.fillStyle = semantic.primary.DEFAULT; // #0f62fe
  ctx.fillRect(0, 0, 100, 100);
}
```

### Chart Example

```typescript
import { semantic } from '$shared/styles/tokens';

const config = {
  datasets: [{
    backgroundColor: semantic.chart[1], // #0f62fe
    borderColor: semantic.primary.DEFAULT,
  }]
};
```

### Programmatic Logic

```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  import { semanticVars } from '$shared/styles/tokens';
  
  let progress = 0.75;
  
  function getColor(val: number) {
    if (val < 0.3) return semanticVars.error.DEFAULT;
    if (val < 0.7) return semanticVars.warning.DEFAULT;
    return semanticVars.success.DEFAULT;
  }
</script>

<div style="width: {progress * 100}%; background: {getColor(progress)}" />
```

---

## ğŸ¨ Component Patterns

### Button

```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  import type { ButtonVariant } from '$shared/styles/tokens';
  export let variant: ButtonVariant = 'primary';
  
  const variants: Record<ButtonVariant, string> = {
    primary: 'bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-primary-foreground',
    secondary: 'bg-secondary hover:bg-secondary-hover text-secondary-foreground',
    destructive: 'bg-destructive hover:bg-destructive-hover text-destructive-foreground',
    accent: 'bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-accent-foreground',
    muted: 'bg-muted hover:bg-muted-hover text-muted-foreground',
  };
</script>

<button class="{variants[variant]} px-4 py-2 rounded-md transition-colors">
  <slot />
</button>
```

### Card

```svelte
<div class="bg-card border border-card-border rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-card-hover transition-colors">
  <slot />
</div>
```

### Input

```svelte
<input 
  class="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-md bg-background text-foreground
         border border-input hover:border-input-hover 
         focus:border-input-focus focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:outline-none
         disabled:bg-muted disabled:opacity-50
         transition-colors"
/>
```

### Badge

```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  import type { StatusVariant } from '$shared/styles/tokens';
  export let variant: StatusVariant = 'info';
  
  const variants: Record<StatusVariant, string> = {
    success: 'bg-success text-success-foreground',
    warning: 'bg-warning text-warning-foreground',
    error: 'bg-error text-error-foreground',
    info: 'bg-info text-info-foreground',
  };
</script>

<span class="{variants[variant]} px-2 py-1 text-sm rounded-md">
  <slot />
</span>
```

---

## âœ… DO / âŒ DON'T

### âœ… DO

```svelte
<!-- Use semantic tokens -->
<button class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground">OK</button>

<!-- Use interactive states -->
<button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover active:bg-primary-active">OK</button>

<!-- Use transitions -->
<button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover transition-colors">OK</button>

<!-- Use foreground for contrast -->
<div class="bg-card text-card-foreground">OK</div>

<!-- Type-safe variants -->
<script lang="ts">
  import type { ButtonVariant } from '$shared/styles/tokens';
  let variant: ButtonVariant = 'primary';
</script>
```

### âŒ DON'T

```svelte
<!-- Hardcoded colors -->
<button class="bg-[#0f62fe]">Wrong</button>
<button style="background: #0f62fe">Wrong</button>

<!-- Primitive tokens directly -->
<button class="bg-blue-60">Wrong</button>

<!-- Semantic.ts instead of Tailwind -->
<button style="background: {semantic.primary.DEFAULT}">Wrong</button>

<!-- Arbitrary spacing -->
<div class="p-[13px]">Wrong</div>

<!-- Bad contrast -->
<button class="bg-primary text-primary">Wrong</button>
```

---

## ğŸ“‹ AI Checklist

Before generating code:

- [ ] Semantic tokens used (not hardcoded colors)
- [ ] Interactive states added (hover/active/disabled)
- [ ] `text-*-foreground` used for proper contrast
- [ ] `transition-colors` added for smooth UX
- [ ] System spacing used (1-13, not arbitrary)
- [ ] System radius used (sm/md/lg/xl)
- [ ] TypeScript types used (ButtonVariant, StatusVariant)
- [ ] Tailwind classes preferred over inline styles

---

## ğŸš€ Quick Patterns

| Component | Pattern |
|-----------|---------|
| **Button** | `bg-{variant} hover:bg-{variant}-hover text-{variant}-foreground px-4 py-2 rounded-md transition-colors` |
| **Card** | `bg-card border border-card-border rounded-lg p-6` |
| **Input** | `border border-input focus:border-input-focus focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring px-3 py-2 rounded-md` |
| **Badge** | `bg-{status} text-{status}-foreground px-2 py-1 text-sm rounded-md` |
| **Sidebar Nav** | `hover:bg-sidebar-hover active:bg-sidebar-active transition-colors` |

